{"tid":2452444,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"紫荊黨公司註冊有變動惹耳語　政界料政改後新舊建制爭位更激","createTime":"2021-03-19T00:02:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T03:39:33.000Z","uid":230530,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"214e2778b152f03217311917fb9c2b3945e6ddb6","tid":2452444,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T00:02:24.000Z","msg":"沉靜了一段時間的紫荊黨，隨著香港選舉制度改革，近日又再活躍。<br />\n<br />\n身兼政協委員的紫荊黨主席李山，在兩會期間接受訪問，大談該黨有意角逐選委及立法會議席，亦強調與建制政黨同是愛國同路人，該黨近期公司註冊出現變動，惹來政界耳語。<br />\n<br />\n去年五月成立的紫荊黨，核心人物還有中播控股主席黃秋智及卓悦主席陳健文，但今年二月，黃秋智及陳健文分別辭去公司秘書及董事。<br />\n<br />\n《政情》向紫荊黨查詢，黃秋智強調兩人並非退黨，強調相關變動為求黨務專業化，並透露紫荊黨將有更多新動向。"},{"pid":"ac4e101c48b1a16fae01a98d3e0f9a4be3192ba1","tid":2452444,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T00:05:07.000Z","msg":"建制派已成condom<br />\n<br />\n紫荊黨先係根正苗紅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/commentaries/dcwatcher/dcwatcher-03102021070941.html/@@images/image\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fcommentaries%2Fdcwatcher%2Fdcwatcher-03102021070941.html%2F%40%40images%2Fimage&h=797bf696&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/17155801/875.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2F17155801%2F875.png&h=25bc6fa2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JEWZT2JXIFD3TMC65ZVEROQBWM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJEWZT2JXIFD3TMC65ZVEROQBWM.jpg&h=4ef276af&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89a719ef24858ecbe6f0e8bde7affae66b4ae003","tid":2452444,"uid":262131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T00:08:25.000Z","msg":"狡兔死 走狗烹<br />\n飛鳥盡 良弓藏<br />\n敵國破 。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\